title: Firefox not working upon opening
content:
Hello,

I having been experiencing this problem for sometime now. I open Firefox application and type-in the desired website: there is no feedback, no loading sign, no error report whatsoever. The attached image shows the exact problem. Please help!

Thank you.
creator: rksbuy

title: Printing dialog
content: Hello, Since the new printing dialog, the preprocessing of the website for printing takes ages (like minutes) to process even simple websites. Is there a way to disable mozillas printing dialog until it is fixed?? impossible to work with ! Also not possible ot stop the processing. Same situation on the windows10 and on OSX 10.12.6 version.
creator: martin.mostboeck

title: metamask show blank white screen <!>
content:
Hi when I click on the Metamask extension it only shows blank white screen. I'm an intuitive linux/computer user meaning; I depend on the computer universal unified consciousness to download what to do and where to go to do anything on a computer. I know nothing right now about web developer options, but I got the techy spidey sense that I need info from developer options to get a clue on how to fix my issue. So the first thing I do is try to highlight invisible text on the blank window that pops up, right click, select all, then I right click again and select view selection source. And then I do the ctrl+shft+j shortcut and I see these two errors pop up in the browser console to see background processes I assume that's what I am looking at.

title: login to meinvodafone
content:
I can call the website vodafone and then click to meinvodafone. If I input Benutzername and Dein Internet-Passwort login starts: OK I tried to store the inputs. Benutzername and Internet-Passwort are correctly stored. But the address is not correctly stored: the adress is reduced! With the stored inputs the login process does not start!

I tried Zugangsdaten hinzufügen and input the correct adress, Benutzername and Internet-Passwort. In the stored data the address is again reduced, Benutzername and Internet-Passwort are correctly stored. No login with the stored data. How can I input the correct address to the stored data?

I tried the login with Microsoft Edge: OK Login with stored data: OK The stored data in Microsoft Edge are correct: Address, Benutzername and Internet-Passwort are corretly stored.

title: Link in email (Thunderbird) won't open in Firefox
content:
Hello.

I am using Ubuntu 21.04 and after the upgrade I got different issues with Mozilla products. FF is: 88.0 64-bit TB is: 78.8.1 (64-Bit)

One is: "Firefox is already running, but is not responding. To use Firefox, you must first close the existing Firefox process, restart your device, or use a different profile." appears if I click on links in emails. It doesn't matter if they're linked to youtube, are an online version of the email etc. Always the same message.

I tried to assign Firefox as a standard browser and changed to another one, started the system again, ran Thunderbird and Firefox and it still happened. I tried changing something in the config editor, doesn't help at all. I checked for files / attachments and what should happen with http/https. There's no entry, which is fine according to mozilla help. The settings are the same as before the upgrade. I don't understand why it doesn't work anymore.

And second problem is: When clicking a email link in Firefox it doesn't open in Thunderbird. Error message is: "Thunderbird is already running, but is not responding. To use Thunderbird, you must first close the existing Thunderbird process, restart your device, or use a different profile."

It also doesn't work if I have run FF and TB in safe mode at the same time or in other constellations (FF in safe mode, TB not and vice versa)

Any other ideas?
creator: antishape

title: Firefox stuck in a corrupted state, opens but nothing else works
